<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>In Pay and Display areas a ticket should be obtained from the ticket machine and be displayed on the windscreen.&lt;br&gt;<br/>In Barrier Controlled areas please take a ticket on entry. If your stay is less than 20 minutes this ticket can be used to exit without charge. Otherwise to exit you will need pay at the barrier.&lt;br&gt;<br/>The charge for parking is £1.60p.</p>
